# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:11
translate spanish micha7a_be31aa9e:

    # "I spend some time talking to Gertrude about the things that have been on my mind. Then when I am about to leave and head to class, she stops me."
    "Me paso un rato hablando con Gertrude sobre las cosas que me rondan por la cabeza. Entonces, cuando estoy a punto de irme a clase, me detiene."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:12
translate spanish micha7a_039a0a46:

    # sc "Hey, before you leave, I wanted to tell you that I talked to Mi-Cha about you."
    sc "Oye, antes de que te vayas, quería decirte que he hablado con Mi-Cha sobre ti."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:13
translate spanish micha7a_ae871f39:

    # pc "Oh yeah?"
    pc "¿Ah, sí?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:14
translate spanish micha7a_13380f5e:

    # sc "She's very shy, but I talked her into having a little coffee meet-up with you. Can you meet her this evening?"
    sc "Es muy tímida, pero la he convencido para que quede contigo a tomar un café. ¿Puedes quedar con ella esta tarde?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:18
translate spanish micha7a_5ec9bea1:

    # sc "Great! I'll let her know to meet you in the school café this evening."
    sc "¡Genial! Le diré que quede contigo en la cafetería de la escuela esta tarde."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:19
translate spanish micha7a_a8af18a8:

    # pc "Cool, I'm looking forward to it."
    pc "Genial, tengo muchas ganas."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:20
translate spanish micha7a_e4769446:

    # sc "Okay, I'll see you later, [pcname]."
    sc "Vale, nos vemos luego, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:23
translate spanish micha7a_9669528e:

    # "Later..."
    "Hasta luego..."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:29
translate spanish micha7a_6750acb1:

    # sc "Oh, I'm sorry. I thought you were."
    sc "Oh, lo siento. Pensaba que lo habías hecho."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:30
translate spanish micha7a_9f1153c2:

    # sc "Okay then. She'll be disappointed, but I'll let her know."
    sc "Vale, entonces. Se llevará una decepción, pero se lo diré."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:31
translate spanish micha7a_9c57fd84:

    # sc "I'll see you later, [pcname]."
    sc "Nos vemos luego, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:39
translate spanish micha7_617439f0:

    # "I head over to the café for my coffee date with Mi-Cha."
    "Me dirijo a la cafetería para mi cita con Mi-Cha."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:44
translate spanish micha7_046f6d25:

    # "When I walk into the café, I spot Mi-Cha sitting alone at one of the tables. She sees me immediately, as if she has been staring at the door waiting for me to enter."
    "Al entrar en la cafetería, veo a Mi-Cha sentada sola en una de las mesas. Me ve enseguida, como si hubiera estado mirando fijamente hacia la puerta esperando a que entrara."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:47
translate spanish micha7_715a3be9:

    # "She immediately stands and walks up towards me."
    "Se levanta inmediatamente y se acerca a mí."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:49
translate spanish micha7_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/micha_7_1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_7_1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:50
translate spanish micha7_b81c6f86:

    # mc "Hello, [pcname]. My name is Mi-Cha. It is very nice to meet you."
    mc "Hola, [pcname]. Me llamo Mi-Cha. Encantada de conocerte."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:51
translate spanish micha7_65b65cd2:

    # pc "Hi, Mi-Cha. We've met already in the lobby remember?"
    pc "Hola, Mi-Cha. Ya nos hemos visto en el vestíbulo, ¿te acuerdas?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:53
translate spanish micha7_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/micha_yes1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_yes1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:54
translate spanish micha7_076877b6:

    # mc "Yes, I remember."
    mc "Sí, me acuerdo."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:55
translate spanish micha7_1d573332:

    # pc "Do you want a coffee?"
    pc "¿Quieres un café?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:57
translate spanish micha7_bf8efb1f:

    # "She doesn't say anything in response, instead just nodding her head slightly."
    "No dice nada en respuesta, solo asiente ligeramente con la cabeza."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:60
translate spanish micha7_b6487666:

    # bn "Hi there. What can I get for you?"
    bn "Hola. ¿Qué te pongo?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:61
translate spanish micha7_fa4d4666:

    # pc "What would you like, Mi-Cha? I'll pay. Anything you want."
    pc "¿Qué te apetece, Mi-Cha? Yo pago. Lo que quieras."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:62
translate spanish micha7_816eccbd:

    # mc "You first, please."
    mc "Tú primero, por favor."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:63
translate spanish micha7_c24a94ff:

    # pc "Okay. I'll have a hot vanilla latte."
    pc "Vale. Yo tomaré un café con leche caliente con vainilla."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:64
translate spanish micha7_0515f2bf:

    # mc "I will have the same."
    mc "Yo tomaré lo mismo."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:65
translate spanish micha7_a4c27a52:

    # bn "Sure thing. Two hot vanilla lattes coming right up."
    bn "Claro. Dos cafés con leche calientes con vainilla, ahora mismo."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:68
translate spanish micha7_9e1b5b12:

    # "We wait for our drinks, I pay, then we go to a table and sit down."
    "Esperamos nuestras bebidas, pago, y luego nos sentamos en una mesa."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:69
translate spanish micha7_c8eefb91:

    # "Mi-Cha doesn't say anything, just looking down at her coffee and smiling nervously."
    "Mi-Cha no dice nada, solo mira su café y sonríe nerviosamente."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:74
translate spanish micha7_2aebf130:

    # mc "Very good, thank you."
    mc "Muy bueno, gracias."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:80
translate spanish micha7_2aebf130_1:

    # mc "Very good, thank you."
    mc "Muy bueno, gracias."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:83
translate spanish micha7_fa75bbc3:

    # pc "Are you okay?"
    pc "¿Estás bien?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:84
translate spanish micha7_dc52a31e:

    # pc "You seem a little nervous."
    pc "Pareces un poco nerviosa."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:86
translate spanish micha7_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/micha_yes2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_yes2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:87
translate spanish micha7_d1bf83b5:

    # mc "Yes. I am."
    mc "Sí. Lo estoy."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:88
translate spanish micha7_fb27d9a1:

    # pc "You don't have to be nervous around me. I'm not going to hurt you."
    pc "No tienes por qué estar nerviosa conmigo. No voy a hacerte daño."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:89
translate spanish micha7_27577933:

    # mc "I know. I really want you to like me."
    mc "Lo sé. De verdad quiero gustarte."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:90
translate spanish micha7_fcf5ae2f:

    # pc "I do like you."
    pc "Me gustas."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:93
translate spanish micha7_81709362:

    # mc "You do?"
    mc "¿De verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:94
translate spanish micha7_423fa223:

    # pc "Sure. That's why I asked Gertrude to set up this date."
    pc "Claro. Por eso le pedí a Gertrude que organizara esta cita."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:95
translate spanish micha7_6af12bd8:

    # mc "This is a date?"
    mc "¿Esto es una cita?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:96
translate spanish micha7_c1f89784:

    # pc "A coffee date, yeah."
    pc "Una cita para tomar un café, sí."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:99
translate spanish micha7_57067727:

    # mc "Not the kind of date that ends in bed though?"
    mc "¿Pero no es el tipo de cita que acaba en la cama?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:102
translate spanish micha7_7d70b936:

    # mc "Good. I do not think I am ready for that yet."
    mc "Bien. No creo que esté preparada para eso todavía."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:104
translate spanish micha7_8d1c80ad:

    # mc "No!"
    mc "¡No!"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:105
translate spanish micha7_8413dde0:

    # mc "I'm sorry. I do not think I am ready for that yet."
    mc "Lo siento. No creo que esté preparada para eso todavía."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:108
translate spanish micha7_7d63d9da:

    # mc "I am very sorry. Did I offend you?"
    mc "Lo siento mucho. ¿Te he ofendido?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:109
translate spanish micha7_8b131ed8:

    # mc "I did not mean I would not want to go to bed with you. But I feel uncomfortable about it right now."
    mc "No quería decir que no quisiera acostarme contigo. Pero ahora mismo me siento incómoda con eso."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:110
translate spanish micha7_0d2c9d39:

    # pc "It's okay, I wasn't suggesting that. You didn't offend me."
    pc "No pasa nada, no estaba sugiriendo eso. No me has ofendido."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:113
translate spanish micha7_0e8b4e1b:

    # mc "Oh no, I am making things worse aren't I?"
    mc "Oh, no, estoy empeorando las cosas, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:114
translate spanish micha7_c767c9ce:

    # mc "I am so bad at this."
    mc "Soy muy mala en esto."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:115
translate spanish micha7_c1e312a1:

    # pc "It's okay, really. Just calm down."
    pc "No pasa nada, de verdad. Tranquila."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:118
translate spanish micha7_87a0b25e:

    # "I reach over and place my hand over hers. She starts to pull away at first, then relaxes."
    "Me acerco y le pongo la mano encima de la suya. Al principio empieza a apartarse, pero luego se relaja."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:121
translate spanish micha7_7c1c3cc4:

    # mc "Miss Spann did not tell me that you asked for this date. I thought that she set it up because she wanted me to meet people."
    mc "La señorita Spann no me dijo que tú hubieras pedido esta cita. Pensaba que ella la había organizado porque quería que conociera a gente."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:122
translate spanish micha7_36fab42e:

    # mc "It does make me feel better that you requested it."
    mc "Me hace sentir mejor saber que tú la pediste."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:123
translate spanish micha7_f3c20824:

    # mc "Why did you want to buy me coffee?"
    mc "¿Por qué querías invitarme a un café?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:124
translate spanish micha7_f0ffbaf0:

    # pc "I don't know. I thought you were cute and could use a friend."
    pc "No lo sé. Me pareciste mona y pensé que te vendría bien una amiga."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:127
translate spanish micha7_41d2c325:

    # mc "You think that I am cute?"
    mc "¿Tú crees que soy mona?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:128
translate spanish micha7_d54e19e4:

    # pc "Yeah. You're very cute."
    pc "Sí. Eres muy mona."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:132
translate spanish micha7_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice 'voices/micha_thankyou1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_thankyou1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:133
translate spanish micha7_5b61e929:

    # mc "Thank you, [pcname]."
    mc "Gracias, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:134
translate spanish micha7_61a02886:

    # mc "I… think that you are cute as well."
    mc "Yo… también creo que eres mona."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:137
translate spanish micha7_3b1b3410:

    # mc "Oh no, I should not have said that. I can't believe I said that."
    mc "Oh, no, no debería haber dicho eso. No puedo creer que lo haya dicho."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:138
translate spanish micha7_84587f43:

    # pc "What? It's okay that you think I'm cute."
    pc "¿Qué? No pasa nada si piensas que soy mona."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:139
translate spanish micha7_a67a4bd1:

    # mc "No. I can't. I should go."
    mc "No. No puedo. Debería irme."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:140
translate spanish micha7_59ee5f3a:

    # pc "Why? You've barely drunk your coffee. I'd like to talk to you more."
    pc "¿Por qué? Apenas te has tomado el café. Me gustaría hablar más contigo."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:142
translate spanish micha7_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice 'voices/micha_imsorry2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_imsorry2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:143
translate spanish micha7_918fea83:

    # mc "I'm sorry."
    mc "Lo siento."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:146
translate spanish micha7_6305b1a7:

    # mc "Is it okay if I leave?"
    mc "¿Te parece bien si me voy?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:151
translate spanish micha7_d7eacc92:

    # mc "I know better than to be so forward."
    mc "Sé que no debo ser tan atrevida."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:152
translate spanish micha7_cafb4599:

    # mc "I have been taught better than to say things like that."
    mc "Me han enseñado que no se deben decir cosas así."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:153
translate spanish micha7_f3946300:

    # mc "I am very sorry, but I would like to go now."
    mc "Lo siento mucho, pero me gustaría irme ahora."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:157
translate spanish micha7_bb0eeaf4:

    # mc "Thank you."
    mc "Gracias."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:158
translate spanish micha7_c5f761de:

    # mc "I'm very sorry."
    mc "Lo siento mucho."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:161
translate spanish micha7_3ac8722a:

    # pc "There's no reason to apologize. You haven't done anything wrong."
    pc "No hay motivo para disculparse. No ha hecho nada malo."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:163
translate spanish micha7_d41d8cd9_5:

    # voice 'voices/micha_thankyou1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_thankyou1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:164
translate spanish micha7_024933de:

    # mc "Thank you. You're very kind."
    mc "Gracias. Es usted muy amable."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:165
translate spanish micha7_26dc8eb0:

    # pc "Can we at least try this again sometime?"
    pc "¿Podemos al menos intentarlo de nuevo alguna vez?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:168
translate spanish micha7_d6451512:

    # "She makes a squeaking sound somewhere deep in her throat, as if the words are being forcefully pushed out."
    "Ella emite un chirrido en lo más profundo de la garganta, como si las palabras salieran a la fuerza."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:169
translate spanish micha7_f800bed0:

    # mc "Yes."
    mc "Sí."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:172
translate spanish micha7_f5c4b536:

    # "Then she practically runs out of the café."
    "Entonces sale prácticamente corriendo de la cafetería."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:175
translate spanish micha7_b95ac3d7:

    # "Well that was definitely one of the weirder first dates I've had. Not sure what was going on with her."
    "Bueno, sin duda ha sido una de las primeras citas más raras que he tenido. No estoy seguro de qué le pasaba."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:176
translate spanish micha7_9788c24f:

    # "But she did say yes to another date."
    "Pero sí que dijo que sí a otra cita."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:179
translate spanish micha7_2b06c7c2:

    # "Maybe that one will go a little more smoothly."
    "Quizá esa vaya un poco mejor."

